This archive contains the TGA File Format Specification manual, version 2.2,
in PostScript form.  tgacont.ps is the table of contents and tgafile.ps is
the body of the manual.  The total length is 30 printed pages.

If you need a printed copy of the manual, call Truevision Customer Service 
at (317) 576-8118 and request a copy be mailed to you.  Also, call 
Truevision's Truelink BBS (317-577-8783, 8N1, 300-9600 Baud) for TGA images,
TGA file manipulation tools, and information on Truevision's line of video
graphics hardware and software.
